#. Tag: para
#: apps_libreoffice.xml:603
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When another person opens the document, the checksum will be generated "
"again. The new checksum is then compared to the original one. If both are "
"equal, the application will signal that the document has not changed in the "
"meantime."
