"にすることができます。"

#. Tag: para
#: apps_libreoffice.xml:659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also assign macros to application events if you want specific "
"actions to occur when those events take place. For example, if you always "
"work with a specific spreadsheet, you can create a macro that opens the "
"spreadsheet and assign the macro to the <guimenu>Start Application</guimenu> "
